Package: refuge
Version: 0.1.0
Title: Locate Trans and Intersex-Friendly Toilets
Description: Access the 'Refuge' API, a web-application for locating trans and 
    intersex-friendly restrooms, including unisex and accessible restrooms. 
    Includes data on the location of restrooms, along with directions, 
    comments, user ratings and amenities. Coverage is global, but most data is 
    in the United States.
    See <https://www.refugerestrooms.org/api/docs/> for full API documentation.
